				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Fire water can be made by any gnome level 16 or above using their tinkering skill, it is already trivial as gnomes start with a tinkering skill of 50 when they reach level 16. Firewater is made by combining Gnomish Spirits with a flask of water (not summoned water)
				</font>
