				Okay just to clarify-gnomes can tinker from birth, at level 16 they can then improve their skills at level my gnome cleric made the following as trivial<BR>
   Firewater, fireworks, collaspible fishing pole, animated bait, and flameless latern. I wont waste yer time with the specifics of each their are books in game that tell you exactly what you need. At level 16 your skill goes up to make, cams, underwater breathing helmet, and there is other stuff to be discovered, but at level one a gnome can make all those listed above. Please enjoy. Fireworks are a blast.
